ent events or newly available information april  spice global type private industry conglomerate predecessor modi corp mcorp global spice corp founded  founder b k modi headquarters singapore india area served worldwide key people ozi amanat cio total assets us  billion  number of employees  website spice global spice global is an indian conglomerate headquartered in singapore the company operates in the sectors of telecom finance entertainment and technology they operate internationally in los angeles new york kuala lumpur london dubai nepal bangladesh uganda tanzania zimbabwe sri lanka and shenzen in  the companys aggregated assets totalled us billion with over  employees worldwide spice global is planning to offer fullfledged banking service with focus on smart banking which is showing a  annual growth to its customers it has applied to the reserve bank of india rbi for a license the company is already offering financial services through wall street finance which has  subagents across india including vijaya bank icici bank and kotak in  the company made an aggressive bid to acquire the american business magazine forbes media from the forbes family and the private equity group elevation partners ozi amanat valued the company and acquisition at –m and quoted it as one of the world’s most brilliant brands the bid for forbes was short listed as the  top bidders for acquisition beating time inc fox bloomberg warren buffett and other major investors contents  history  proposed operations  awards and honors  subsidiaries  board of directors  references  external links historyedit spice global was established in  by b k modi under the name modi corp later the company came to be known as mcorp global and spice corp before it finally became spice global in  a bid between virgin mobile and spice global was held for the g contract of mahanagar telephone nigam limited the deal was eventually called off due to regulation issues and a deal was not signed for the network spice telecom was sold to idea cellular in  the company abandoned plans for a us  million ipo when the dubai financial market general index dropped  percent in  the decision where to hold the ipo was withheld from the general public with singapore hong kong london and the us as strongly speculated possibilities however plans in  revealed spice global would be listed in london modi expects to raise us  billion in the listing where london has agreed to the listing proposed operationsedit spice global group plans to expand its footprint in malaysia spice global has a presence in malaysia in the field of mobile software and hardware technology through spice csl spice global had earlier taken over the malaysian mobile company csl the company did a business worth over us million in malaysia in  and hopes to breach us million rm million by  this year spice csl will launch two new smartphones and one tablet in malaysia the company is currently in talks with malayan banking bhd maybank and bank islam malaysia bhd for strategic partnerships for its proposed banking business spice global is interested in entering the malaysian healthcare sector and is in talks with ihh healthcare bhd for a partnership the company also plans to buy a property in putrajaya awards and honorsedit  golden peacock certificates for innovative productsservices global premier of the worlds first movie phone  peoples phone at the world mobile congress barcelona product of the year innovation award  spice mobility ranked  in asias  best under a billion subsidiariesedit sii mobility sii  representing mobility businesses outside india listed in singapore stock exchange sgx m s mobility limited – representing mobility businesses in india listed in nse nse spicemobil and bse bse  spice retail  telecommunications retail and accessory chain  stores in  cities spice digital  business solutions for telecom operators spice csl  global spice mobility and is based in malaysia it enjoys a market share of  in malaysia spice